            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <figcaption class="dt-phone-cap"><b>Standard: record table becomes key/value cards.</b> Each card is one attendee, a real list with real label text. The recommended default when users read one record at a time.</figcaption>
    </figure>

    <figure class="dt-phone-fig" aria-hidden="true">
      <div class="dt-phone">
        <div class="dt-phone-screen">
          <div class="dt-phone-island"></div>
