      <figcaption class="dt-phone-cap"><b>Standard: comparison stays a table, scroll horizontally.</b> The Name column is pinned with <code>position: sticky</code>; the rest runs off the right edge. The default when comparing values across columns is the task.</figcaption>
    </figure>
  </div>

  <div class="dt-demo">
    <div class="dt-demo-label">Live: Pattern A, focusable scroll region with a sticky first column</div>
    <p class="dt-filter-status" style={{ 'margin-top': 0, 'margin-bottom': '0.6rem' }}>Tab to the table below, then scroll it sideways. The Attendee column stays pinned.</p>
    <div
      class="dt-scroll"
      role="region"
